        {
            "title": "散戶投資者在市場波動加劇時轉為賣方,Citadel Securities表示",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/JkT.J6EQ.Cm0QnT5ytAxjQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXMPEA7306L_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com - 根據Citadel Securities平台數據,散戶投資者上週轉為美國股票和期權的淨賣方,這標誌著他們近年來持續買入行為的轉變。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Citadel Securities股票及股票衍生品策略主管Scott Rubner表示,個人交易者上週賣出美國股票和期權。自2020年1月以來,該公司僅記錄到18次類似的賣出活動。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">散戶投資者的淨名義支出在3月較前一個月下降約55%,較1月的峰值下降約70%,儘管散戶投資者在上個月仍保持淨買入狀態。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-77dee8b8-aa45-3cf6-85ed-d046560c2db4-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Citadel Securities數據顯示,散戶賣出期間歷來與美國股市短期回報走強相關。在類似信號出現後的兩個月內,標普500指數約有82%的時間上漲,平均漲幅為4.1%。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">散戶交易者的期權活動也在發生變化。儘管交易量仍處於高位,但持倉已轉向更具防禦性,上週資金流向略微偏向賣出,對下行保護的需求增加。根據Citadel Securities數據,上週是自11月底以來散戶期權活動首次出現看跌的一週。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">機構持倉也變得更具防禦性,儘管這種調整開始得更早。Rubner在週二給客戶的報告中寫道,系統性策略相對於改善的已實現波動率狀況仍處於低配狀態,隨著市場企穩,這為增量買入資金流創造了潛力。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這一轉變發生在油價飆升和伊朗戰爭引發數週波動之後。隨著中東衝突升級擾亂能源市場,標普500指數在3月下跌約5%。布蘭特原油今年已上漲約80%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
